==Twin towns – sister cities==

Roman is twinned with:
* Dilijan, Armenia
* Edineț, Moldova
* Gedera, Israel
* Grugliasco, Italy
* Ștefan Vodă, Moldova
* Sunchang, South Korea
* Samothraki, Greece
