<doc id="415863" wikidata="Q607550" url="?curid=415863" title="Leforest">
<text>Leforest () is a commune in the Pas-de-Calais department in the Hauts-de-France region of France about east of Lens.

==Population==
The inhabitants are called &quot;Leforestois&quot;.
==See also==
*Communes of the Pas-de-Calais department

